Mary Auma, mother to former Harambee Stars captain Dennis Oliech is dead. Auma died on Friday at her home in Lavington after developing difficulty in breathing. Mama Oliech as she was popularly known was also receiving treatment for cancer. The body has been moved to Umash Funeral Home. The late Auma was also popular for her famous ‘Mama Oliech’ restaurant which she managed. More to follow. 